            brought together everything I love, on one hand the creation of a
            product that impacts people's lives, and on the other hand my more
            creative approach, those two passions helped me to find UX/UI
            design. Since then, I have been in constant search of new ways of
            expression and how to merge functionality with aesthetics in every
            project I embark on.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class='mt-10'>
